quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  76,6,"Sewnde nde jiyaa…ìe Alla …ìallinaa…ìe njarata he…ìe ilnande ilnugol."
  76,7,"He…ìe kuu…ìna takkere ho…ìe kula √±alawma mbo bone mum na saroo."
  76,8,"Ho…ìe √±ammina √±amri wond'ude e yi…óde ndi miskiin e alyatiime e dahaa…óo."
  76,9,"Miin √±amminirta mon ko sabi Alla miin faalaaka e mon njo…ìdi wona yetteede."
  76,10,"Pellet min kuli ummaade e joomi amen ko √±alawma √±ir…ìinii…óo cattu…óo tumminaare."
  76,11,"Alla reeni…ìe e bone oon √±alawma o okki…ìe pummam laba…óam e weltaare."
  76,12,"Alla yo…ìiri …ìe ko…ìe mu√±i ko aljanna e (comci)hariir."
  76,13,"Ho…ìe tuugnii e fotooyji …ìe yi'atah heen na'ange wonah jaangol cattungol."
  76,14,"Na …ìadi e dow mu'en …óowdi mammba …ìesnaa…óe mum na eeltanaa…ìe eeltegol."
  76,15,"Ina taarnee…ìe ngennduwo√± kaalis e kaasyo√± na feewnira weer."
  76,16,"Ka'aseeje kaalis ho…óe potndira potndegol."
  76,17,"Ho…ìe njarnee kaas njilludi mum ko janjabiil."
  76,18,"Sewnde na e hembo na innire Sal sabiil."
  76,19,"Sukaa…ìe saasnaa…ìe na mbanngo e mum en si a yi'ii…ìe cikka ko …ìe lu'u lu'u caraa…óo."
  76,20,"Si a yi'i toon nji'a neema e laamu manngu."
  76,21,"Ina e dow mu'en comci sundus …ói mbaadi ha'aka hecco e istabraq …ìe …ìoorna jawe kaalis joom mu'en yarna…ìe njaram laa…ì…óam."
  76,22,"Pellet …óum wonanii mon njo…ìdi golle mon kadi golle mon ngoniina mantaa…óe."
  76,23,"Ko minen tigi tellini alquraana e dow ma tellingol."
  76,24,"Mu√± e √±aawoore joom ma woto …óofto e mum en bakkadin…óo wolla ke'efeera."
  76,25,"ja≈ãta inne joom ma subaka e kikii…óa."